2. Didactic
3. Technology ({ICT})
4. Diversity
5. Accessibility
These recommendations are intended to guide the teacher in the pro-
cess of developing or updating an {OER} specifically in each particular
dimension, thus ensuring its quality. Each recommendation has a set
of questions associated as a checklist for assessing the product. They
are based on the previous bibliography, citing the source.
